      "content": "rebuilding... thats what people say to make it sound better, but they don't get it. you can't rebuild a person. the version of me that mattered is gone. people don't see a person in recovery, they just see a failure. there's no path back to being \"someone\" again. i've just been existing, but there's nothing actually there anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
